# Widget image delivery

Read `AGENTS.md` → section **CRITICAL: «не вдається завантажити віджет»** before editing these files.

## MUST

- Deliver widget photos via `setImageViewBitmap` only (`PhotoWidgetRenderer`).
- Render offline in `WidgetImageCache`; bake shape into bitmap.
- Keep `MAX_BITMAP_BYTES` ≈ 2_100_000 (RGB_565) unless tested on Android 17+ (Pixel/Nexus Launcher).
- Apply EXIF in `ImageOrientationHelper`; sync preview via `WidgetImagePreview`.

## MUST NOT

- `setImageViewUri` for widget `ImageView` (breaks Android 17: `AppsFilter: BLOCKED`).
- `setViewOutlinePreferredRadius` / `setClipToOutline` on RemoteViews.
- Jetpack Glance for this widget.
- Uncompressed full-resolution bitmaps through Binder.

## Quality

Improve inside the byte budget: RGB_565 for opaque rectangle+cover; ARGB with transparent corners for rounded/circle/contain. Do not use `#121212` under shape clips. Do not switch to FileProvider/URI.
